title: LF ADC Main to Duo, Plat 3+
body:
G'day lads,

As the title suggest,
I'm looking for an adc main P3 - D4 who is keen to duo Q, 
it's balls out there supporting random adcs every match.
Finished D5 in S6.

Mic + Discord
18+
Good banter
Online everyday (Holidays bitch)
In it for the grind, can't win every match.

Add me,

ix sonic x
